race.comment: LISA'S VOGUE (6) was below best last time when sixth but three back was a Grade 5 winner in quick time at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a tricky draw. Expecting significant improvement. WOOPI BLUEBIRDS (3) is having her first look at this track. Scored last start (19.43) at Muswellbrook over 336m. Expected to measure up again. SMACK WATER MAN (1) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Grade 5 winner three back (19.80) at Muswellbrook over 336m. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the rails draw. Can turn it around this time. CRANKY CRUISER (8) has a solid strike rate at this distance.
